                            <comment id="13175402" author="lacostej" created="Fri, 23 Dec 2011 12:29:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix with an integration test. Depends on various bugs having beeing fixed. e.g. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TIKA-830&quot; title=&quot;Tika.parseToString() causes ForkParser to try to serialize itself&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;TIKA-830&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;TIKA-830&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13175935" author="gagravarr" created="Mon, 26 Dec 2011 12:52:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix committed in r1224728.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve also committed the tests, but I&apos;ve had to leave one disabled as other ForkParser issues means we can enable it just yet&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13176068" author="gagravarr" created="Tue, 27 Dec 2011 02:46:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve enabled the last test in r1224864 - I had to switch it to not use the Tika facade (as that&apos;s not supported for the ForkedParser)&lt;/p&gt;

